4224	1086	|Poky Build Tool|\n|---|\n|BitBake Tool (bitbake)|\n|OpenEmbedded Core (meta)|\n|Poky Distribution Metadata (meta-poky)|\n|Yocto Project Reference BSP (meta-yocto-bsp)|	text	txt	2024-07-28 10:06:54.995753	2
