5096	1472	We can lock/unlock the spinlock using `spin_lock()` and `spin_unlock()` inline functions, both defined in `include/linux/spinlock.h`:	text	txt	2024-07-28 10:09:22.325193	1
5097	1472	static __always_inline void spin_unlock(spinlock_t *lock);\nstatic __always_inline void spin_lock(spinlock_t *lock);	code	txt	2024-07-28 10:09:22.339809	2
