2524	790	The `always` policy always restarts a stopped container unless it has been\nexplicitly stopped. However, if you restart the Docker daemon, the container\nwill be automatically restarted when the daemon comes back up.	text	txt	2024-07-28 09:52:19.192263	1
2525	790	docker container run --interactive --tty --restart always alpine /bin/bash	code	txt	2024-07-28 09:52:19.213008	2
