2527	791	The main difference between the `always` and `unless-stopped` policies is\nthat containers with the `unless-stopped` policy will not be restarted when\nthe daemon restarts if they were in the `Stopped (Exited)` state.	text	txt	2024-07-28 09:52:19.552197	1
