3777	1186	You first put a specific parameter in `eax`, then execute the instruction\n`cpuid`, and finally check the returned value in `ecx` and `edx`. Indeed,\n`cpuid` uses 32-bit registers.	text	txt	2024-07-28 09:55:41.878164	1
